ue">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-12/ty-article/.premium/at-intl-court-of-justice-israel-presents-robust-defense-despite-half-wit-politicians/0000018c-fdaa-d517-af9d-fdbe8aee0000</guid></item><item><title>针对以色列的“战线统一”也增强了伊朗国内代理人的地位</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-01-12/ty-article/.premium/the-unity-of-fronts-against-israel-also-enhanced-status-of-irans-proxies-domestically/0000018c-fd6e-d517-af9d-fd7e6f1a0000</link><description>真主党、也门胡塞武装和伊拉克什叶派民兵组织已经在国内的战斗中取得了成果，而且他们并不打算在加沙战争结束后停止。</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jan 2024 14:05:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-01-12/ty-article/.premium/the-unity-of-fronts-against-israel-also-enhanced-status-of-irans-proxies-domestically/0000018c-fd6e-d517-af9d-fd7e6f1a0000</guid></item><item><title>一系列失败证明以色列安全理念已经过时</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-12/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/a-series-of-failures-proves-that-israels-security-concept-is-obsolete/0000018c-fda7-d517-af9d-fdbff7850000</link><description>情报一次又一次失败，现在两线作战，平民后方遭受前所未有的攻势。以色列国防军的威慑力曾有效应对 20 世纪 60 年代的威胁，但如今需要不同的解决方案。旧制度已经破产</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jan 2024 13:19:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-12/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/a-series-of-failures-proves-that-israels-security-concept-is-obsolete/0000018c-fda7-d517-af9d-fdbff7850000</guid></item><item><title>五十万加沙人正在遭受严重饥饿。让其沉入其中</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-12/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/half-a-million-gazans-are-suffering-from-acute-hunger-let-that-sink-in/0000018c-fd57-d517-af9d-fd7f19b10000</link><description>加沙危机的范围变得越来越清晰；据联合国称，以色列正在创造条件，使加沙的生活变得不可能；但以色列领导人却毫不在意</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jan 2024 12:29:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-12/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/half-a-million-gazans-are-suffering-from-acute-hunger-let-that-sink-in/0000018c-fd57-d517-af9d-fd7f19b10000</guid></item><item><title>3亿年前早期爬行动物的皮肤化石展示了从海洋到陆地的转变</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/science/2024-01-12/ty-article/earliest-skin-fossil-showcases-transition-from-sea-to-land/0000018c-fd0d-d2fd-a3ae-fd0f8bcc0000</link><description>爬行动物祖先的指甲大小的皮肤是迄今为止在陆地动物身上发现的最早的皮肤化石，可能展示了原始状态</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jan 2024 10:47:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/science/2024-01-12/ty-article/earliest-skin-fossil-showcases-transition-from-sea-to-land/0000018c-fd0d-d2fd-a3ae-fd0f8bcc0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡永无休止的任期是以色列的毒瘤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-12/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-never-ending-tenure-is-israels-malignant-disease/0000018c-fa20-d517-af9d-fe3e08560000</link><description>随着以色列与哈马斯的战争即将进入第 100 天，政府必须将遣返人质作为首要任务 - 即使以停火为代价。 ■ 哈马斯通过其外交/法律手段将以色列拖到国际法院开普敦代理——突显内塔尼亚胡政府在各方面的失败程度</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jan 2024 04:00:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-12/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-never-ending-tenure-is-israels-malignant-disease/0000018c-fa20-d517-af9d-fe3e08560000</guid></item><item><title>以色列与哈马斯的战争已接近100天。未来还有很多天的战斗</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-12/ty-article/.premium/digging-in-hamas-isnt-giving-up-idf-far-from-achieving-its-goals/0000018c-f9d3-dd94-a9cc-fbff27910000</link><description>哈马斯正在顽强抵抗，而以色列国防军远未实现其目标 ■ 以色列对新人质协议说“不”可能会导致他们的灭亡 ■ 美国国务卿为第二天制定了自己的计划 - 但有一个小问题</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jan 2024 04:00:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-12/ty-article/.premium/digging-in-hamas-isnt-giving-up-idf-far-from-achieving-its-goals/0000018c-f9d3-dd94-a9cc-fbff27910000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡：药品将在“未来几天”转移给加沙的以色列人质</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-12/ty-article-live/israel-to-counter-south-african-genocide-accusations-at-international-court-of-justice/0000018c-fbaa-dd94-a9cc-fbeeb7c10000</link><description>以色列向联合国最高法院提出针对种族灭绝指控的诉讼，猛烈抨击南非“严重歪曲事实和法律” ■ 以色列国防军表示将启动军事机制，调查涉嫌在加沙违反国际法的行为 ■ 美国和英国发动袭击在红海航运遭受数月袭击后，伊朗支持的也门胡塞武装；胡塞武装发誓，这次袭击不会逃脱惩罚。 ■ 黎巴嫩总理表示，不包括加沙停火的协议毫无意义；从黎巴嫩向以色列北部发射的反坦克导弹</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jan 2024 03:31:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-12/ty-article-live/israel-to-counter-south-african-genocide-accusations-at-international-court-of-justice/0000018c-fbaa-dd94-a9cc-fbeeb7c10000</guid></item><item><title>“在我按照与生俱来的权利去以色列旅行之前，我并不关心自己是不是犹太人。然后我的整个世界都变了”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2024-01-12/ty-article/.highlight/i-didnt-care-about-being-jewish-until-i-went-on-birthright-my-whole-world-changed/0000018c-fb82-dd94-a9cc-fbee842a0000</link><description>本周在本古里安机场：一名美国人在遇到一系列先知后决定成为一名拉比，而一个以色列家庭在父亲完成加沙几个月的预备役后正在休息</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jan 2024 02:58:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2024-01-12/ty-article/.highlight/i-didnt-care-about-being-jewish-until-i-went-on-birthright-my-whole-world-changed/0000018c-fb82-dd94-a9cc-fbee842a0000</guid></item><item><title>台上台下，奥哈德·纳哈林在加沙战争中传达了强有力的信息</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-12/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/on-stage-and-off-ohad-naharin-conveys-a-powerful-message-amid-gaza-war/0000018c-fb01-d517-af9d-ff3fc49a0000</link><description>“人们称我为以色列的诽谤者，但诽谤以色列这个定居者救世主右翼的是我们的政府。他们认为以色列国防军的行动应该继续下去，士兵和人质的死亡是可以理解的代价。巴特谢瓦舞蹈团编舞家奥哈德·纳哈林拒绝闭嘴跳舞</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jan 2024 02:29:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-12/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/on-stage-and-off-ohad-naharin-conveys-a-powerful-message-amid-gaza-war/0000018c-fb01-d517-af9d-ff3fc49a0000</guid></item><item><title>美国：伊朗是胡塞武装和其他组织袭击以色列的主要推动者</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-12/ty-article/u-s-iran-is-primary-enabler-of-houthis-and-other-groups-attacking-israel/0000018c-fb6d-d517-af9d-ff7fb9bb0