scribe-being-shunned-by-global-community-after-october-7/0000018c-f92a-dd94-a9cc-fbee4d680000</guid></item><item><title>随着国际航空公司恢复飞往以色列的航班，价格下降</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article/.premium/prices-drop-as-international-airlines-resume-flights-to-israel/0000018c-f95d-dd94-a9cc-fbfd0b7c0000</link><description>飞往以色列的航班竞争加剧，导致机票价格较12月份全面大幅下跌，而飞往尚未竞争的目的地的票价则保持不变</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 17:40:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article/.premium/prices-drop-as-international-airlines-resume-flights-to-israel/0000018c-f95d-dd94-a9cc-fbfd0b7c0000</guid></item></channel></rss>